1. Robot starts moving forward (3 seconds)
Both motors spin forward
Robot goes straight ahead
2. Robot turns left (2 seconds)
Left motor reverses
Right motor moves forward
Robot rotates left (on the spot or in an arc)
3. Robot turns right (2 seconds)
Left motor moves forward
Right motor reverses
Robot rotates right
4. Robot moves backward (3 seconds)
Both motors reverse
Robot goes straight backward
5. Robot stops
Motors stop completely
No movement
